your hand holding the begging-pot, go ask for food; <span
class="margnote">. 2052</span>

'On every side the living perish, what room for indolence? the worldly
man, relying on his substance or his family, indulging in indolence, is
wrong; <span class="margnote">. 2053</span>

'How much more the religious man, whose purpose is to seek the way of
