religious, and practises the way of straight behaviour, a false and
crooked way of speech is not becoming. <span class="margnote">.
2055</span>

'False and flattering speech is like the magician's

<span id="page_301">p. 301</span>

art; but he who ponders on religion cannot speak falsely (wildly). To
